BT 0.15 g /F1 10 Tf 72 490 Td (PRINCIPLE 3: Track what matters. What gets measured gets managed. The trackers in this) Tj ET
BT 0.15 g /F1 10 Tf 72 476 Td (chapter make it easy to see your progress.) Tj ET
